'''第四次德拉省戰役'''，又名'''2015年1月德拉省攻勢'''，是[[敘利亞反對派|敘利亞反對派]]為了奪取政府軍於[[德拉省|德拉省]]{{link-en|艾夏赫瑪斯金|Al-Shaykh Maskin}}（Al-Shaykh Maskin）的營地，所發動的軍事攻擊<ref name="start"/>。反對派意圖藉此確保德拉省至[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]高速公路的控制權<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/PetoLucem/status/528571612308963330|title=Peto Lucem on Twitter|work=Twitter|accessdate=2014-12-04|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410143729/https://twitter.com/petolucem/status/528571612308963330|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及自身在德拉省的各個據點<ref name="battles"/>。

== 反對派攻勢 ==
2015年1月24日，反對派發表了在德拉省進行的三項戰鬥：

* "勝利僅來自阿拉"<ref name="start"/>
* "踢破門而入"<ref name="battles"/>
* "充滿聯合"<ref name="battles"/>

當天，十名反對派民兵（包含一名戰場指揮官）戰死<ref name="start">{{cite web|url=http://syriahr.com/en/2015/01/9-fighter-killed-in-daraa-and-the-islamic-and-rebel-factions-announce-start-of-new-battle/|title=10 fighters killed in Daraa, and the Islamic and rebel factions announce start of new battle|author=sohranas|work=Syrian Observatory For Human Rights|accessdate=2015-01-26|archive-date=2015-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128212708/http://syriahr.com/en/2015/01/9-fighter-killed-in-daraa-and-the-islamic-and-rebel-factions-announce-start-of-new-battle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔天，反對派突破了政府軍第82旅的防線，攻下其基地<ref name="battles">{{cite web|url=http://www.orient-news.net/?page=news_show&id=84625|title=أورينت نت - تحرير اللواء 82 في درعا..مدينة الشيخ مسكين محررة بالكامل|publisher=|accessdate=2015-01-26|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004155845/http://www.orient-news.net/?page=news_show&id=84625|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據媒體報導，反對派同時佔領城鎮西北方的雷達基地<ref name="alaan"/>。至少有40人在戰鬥中陣亡<ref name="brigade82HQcapt">{{cite web|url=http://syriahr.com/en/2015/01/the-nusra-front-several-rebel-and-islamic-factions-seize-the-brigade-82/|title=The Nusra Front, several rebel and Islamic factions seize the Brigade 82|author=sohranas|work=Syrian Observatory For Human Rights|accessdate=2015-01-26|archive-date=2015-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128041032/http://syriahr.com/en/2015/01/the-nusra-front-several-rebel-and-islamic-factions-seize-the-brigade-82/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾瑪斯達新聞（Al-Masdar News）則表示，14名政府軍於棄守第82旅基地前已戰死<ref name="brigade82capture">{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/daraa-al-nusra-front-captures-brigade-82-base/|title=Dara'a: The Al-Nusra Front Captures Brigade 82 Base|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2015-01-26|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116040834/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/daraa-al-nusra-front-captures-brigade-82-base/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。反對派宣稱在政府軍撤退後，他們隨時可拿下艾夏赫瑪斯金<ref name="alaan">{{cite web|url=http://www.alaan.tv/news/world-news/123150/largest-rebel-victories-shield-two-hundred-people-killed-daraa|title=الثوار في درعا يسيطرون على مدينة الشيخ مسكين واللواء 82 بالكامل|work=Al Aan TV|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702153438/http://www.alaan.tv/news/world-news/123150/largest-rebel-victories-shield-two-hundred-people-killed-daraa|archive-date=2015-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[阿拉伯衛星電視台|阿拉伯衛星電視台]]則說第82旅基地易手後，反對派奪得了附近大部分城鎮<ref name="overran">{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/01/25/Syria-rebels-overtake-strategic-base-in-south.html |title=Syria rebels overtake strategic base in south |accessdate=2015-02-05 |archive-date=2018-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107104143/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/01/25/Syria-rebels-overtake-strategic-base-in-south.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1月29日。反對派推進到艾蘇海里耶（Al-Suhayliyyeh）和第里（Dilli）附近，並攻下艾夏赫瑪斯金北邊的農田。然而，根據艾瑪斯達新聞的報導指出，政府軍已奪回法隆儲存設施和第里的營地，且在{{link-en|瑪利哈艾阿塔什|Maliha al-Atash}}（Maliha al-Atash）擊退反對派的攻擊<ref name="newcasualties">{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/rebel-offensive-intensifies-daraa-syrian-army-recaptures-faroun-storage-facility/|title=Rebel offensive intensifies in Daraa; Syrian Army recaptures Faroun Storage Facility|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2015-02-01|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116135148/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/rebel-offensive-intensifies-daraa-syrian-army-recaptures-faroun-storage-facility/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩天過後，政府軍針對第82旅基地發動反擊，宣稱已收復製氧工廠和尼卡塔艾瑪薩拉特（Niqta Al-Masarat）並向基地北方入口推進。然而，政府軍被迫從基地北方撤退重整。另一方面，反對派也向第里村中心推進<ref name="counter">{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/daraa-syrian-army-attempts-counter-rebels-battalion-82/|title=Dara'a: Syrian Army Attempts to Counter Rebels at Battalion 82|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2015-02-01|archive-date=2019-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211051955/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/daraa-syrian-army-attempts-counter-rebels-battalion-82/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月31日，[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]從空拍確認雷達基地已被反對派攻佔<ref name="radarbase"/>。

